CHANGES
========
0.104.2 - May 2022
Relax javascript check in PDF

0.104.1 - Mar. 2022
Add feature: wildcard support for MIME settings

0.103.4 - Mar. 2022
Fix SAR file content scan
Add option for PDF active content

0.103.3 - July 2021
Remove own default settings from VsaGetConfig and rely on clamav defaults
Change default virusname in case clamav does not return any virus name.

0.103.2 - June 2021
Limit pcre matcher

0.103.0 - April 2021
Increase Version because tested with latest clam engine
Support new parameter SCANHEURISTICLEVEL 

0.101.9 - Jan. 2021
Enhance JPEG check

0.101.8
0.101.7 - Apr. 2020
Fix html check

0.101.6 - Mar. 2020
Use short for for office MIME types

0.101.5 - Dec. 2019
Use libmagic for buffer scan

0.101.4 - Dec. 2019
Direct integration of libmagic.

0.101.3 - Dec. 2019
Correct MIME type name from libmagic.

0.101.2 - Dec. 2019
Fix multibyte text type detection

0.101.1 - Nov. 2019
Improve load of libclamav on linux 0.101.1

0.101.0 - Nov. 2019
Fix interface change from clamav 0.101.x

-------------------
0.100.2 - Nov. 2019
-------------------
Fix parser of SAR files
Fix MIME detection for TEXT files

0.99.25 - 20. Dec 2016
-------------------------
Add Office Mime Detected, to be independent from libmagic

0.99.2 - 30. Jun 2016
-------------------------
Fix compare of block extension, soves https://sourceforge.net/p/clamsap/bugs/2/

0.99.1 - 20. Feb 2016
-------------------------
[WIN] fix load of libclamav.dll

0.99.0 - 04. Feb 2016
-------------------------
Check for SAR extract

0.98.9 - 11. November 2015
-------------------------
Improve MIME check
Fix SAP archive decompression

0.98.8 - 21. October 2015
-------------------------
Fix for internal MIME check

0.98.7 - 18. September 2015
-------------------------
Enhance error messages in case of initialisation errors.
Create default sym.link for libclamdsap

0.9.86 - 30. May 2015
-------------------------
Fix problem, if libmagic can not be found in VsaStartup
Security fix for compression, see CVE-2015-2282 and CVE-2015-2278
Enhance buffer scan in libclamdsap

0.9.8  - 30. March 2015
-------------------------
Support of NW-VSI 2.00
This includes the support of MIME type detection in addition to AV.
Use code from SAP example adapter to provide SAP archive format scan.
see http://scn.sap.com/docs/DOC-7838

0.9.74 - 20. April 2012
-------------------------
Allow to connect are remote clam daemon (clamd)
Configure the remote clam daemon with parameter INITSERVERS (server:port)
Configure with parameter SCANACCESSFILELOCAL if the remote clam daemon can
access a local file locally (via NFS / Samba)

0.9.7 - 25. March 2011
-------------------------
Adaptation for ClamAV 0.97
Prevent multiple byte code initialisation

0.9.6 - 01. November 2010
-------------------------
Adaptation for ClamAV 0.96.x

0.9.5 - 05. August 2009
-----------------------
Release library vsclamd (for clamd) and Adaptation for ClamAV 0.95

0.9.1 - 18. August 2008
-----------------------
Minor improvements for misc. compiler
Test on Linux (x86, x86_64), Sun Solaris, Windows

0.9.0 - 15. August 2008
-----------------------
Initial release of beta library vsclam

